data.description: Introducing an extraordinary three-level property offering 6 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and an impressive  living space. This remarkable home is situated in a prime location that is just minutes away from popular restaurants like Green Eggs Cafe, Champs Diner, and Strictly Seafood, making dining options convenient and diverse. Additionally, the proximity to Temple University and the lively atmosphere of Broad Street ensures an exciting and vibrant lifestyle.  Enter and be welcomed by stunning bay windows that fill the space with natural light. This home features new flooring and tasteful modern finishes throughout, creating a stylish and inviting atmosphere. With generously sized rooms and ample storage, this home is ideal for growing families or individuals in need of extra space for work or hobbies. The six bedrooms ensure everyone has their own private sanctuary, offering both privacy and flexibility.  Additionally, the property boasts two beautifully designed bathrooms with upscale finishes.  One of the stand-out features of this home is its expansive enclosed backyard, providing a private oasis for relaxation and hosting guests. Whether you're grilling in the summer or enjoying cozy evenings by the fire pit in the beautiful autumn weather, this outdoor space offers endless possibilities for enjoyment.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this incredible property yours and enjoy the best that this desirable location has to offer. Contact us today to schedule a private tour and experience the true potential of this charming and modern family home!
